## **How We Help**

::: {.callout-note icon="false"}
## {{< iconify bi shield-check >}} **Emergency Support**
Immediate assistance for housing, food, and safety needs
:::

::: {.callout-note icon="false"}
## {{< iconify bi people >}} **Community Connection**
Connecting asylum seekers with local trans-affirming resources
:::

::: {.callout-note icon="false"}
## {{< iconify bi briefcase >}} **Legal Aid Navigation**
Guidance through the complex asylum process
:::

